summary: BTS Reaction: S/O is a self-made millionaire!
body:
BTS Reaction: S/O is a self-made millionaire!

Jin would be on top of the world, I mean he is already the handsomest man in the world, but now his s/o is literally one of the most successful people in the world, like could he ask for a better partner? Honestly, he is truly your biggest hype man in the entire world. 

Suga would truly admire this aspect about you because he knows how hard-working you have to be and how intelligent, too. He is truly impressed and is full of admiration when it comes to you and your career. 

J-Hope would be another that was constantly hyping you and bragging about you to anyone and everyone. He was extremely proud of you and wanted to make sure that others realize how amazing you are. He would market you to a lot of people because he believes that everyone needs to invest in your business since you are so amazing. 

RM found it absolute sexy to see how independent you are. You oozed with confidence and intelligence, things that RM wants in a partner and you had all of it. He would always praise you and make sure you knew how extremely proud he is of you and that he is always supporting you and behind you no matter what. 

Jimin would feel a little jealous, He wants to be able to spoil you and provide for you, but he felt intimidated by your career. BUT he would get over it and still spoil you and overload you with all his love and affection and support for you and your career. 

V would be super shocked when he heard this because you are as equally goofy as he is, but he loves the fact that you have a fun and goofy side but you also are serious and get work done. He loves a hardworking s/o. 

Jungkook would constantly be bragging to all his members about what a talented and successful s/o he has.
